        ]
      },
      "date": "2016-03-15 15:03:25.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nTests uploaded by Trevis Autotest2 from trevis-42vm1 for review-dne-part-1 received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.7/x86_64: (https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sessions/caf3c3b0-eabe-11e5-a573-5254006e85c2). Ran 11 tests.  4 tests failed: lustre-rsync-test, recovery-small, conf-sanity, sanity.",
